DMA Controller

Flags:
  -SINK_MASTER_ADDR       [8]:    DMA must use the address provided by the sink
                                  If not set the DMA uses the address set by the user
  -SOURCE_MASTER_ADDR     [7]:    DMA must use the address provided by the source
                                  If not set the DMA uses the address set by the user
  -DMA_ENABLE             [6]:    Enable DMA Channel
  -PPFIFO_WB_SEL          [5]:    Select between a Ping Pong FIFO or the wishbone bus as the sink
  -SINK_ADDR              [3:0]:  Address of the sink address within DMA
